---
import TopBar from '../components/TopBar.svelte';
import TabStrip from '../components/TabStrip.svelte';
import StatusBar from '../components/StatusBar.svelte';
import SupportPanel from '../components/SupportPanel.svelte';
import CommandPalette from '../components/CommandPalette.svelte';
import ConvertTab from '../components/ConvertTab.svelte';
import ChunkTab from '../components/ChunkTab.svelte';
import EditorTab from '../components/EditorTab.svelte';
import UtilitiesTab from '../components/UtilitiesTab.svelte';
import '../styles/globals.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0e1116" />

  <title>convertFlow — Free JSONL Fine-Tuning Data Converter & RAG Chunker for LLMs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Convert datasets to JSONL for OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral, Llama fine-tuning. Chunk docs for RAG. 17 utilities. 100% in-browser, no signup, no upload. Free." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="JSONL converter, fine-tuning dataset, ChatML to Alpaca, ShareGPT converter, Harmony format, RAG chunking, OpenAI fine-tuning, Anthropic fine-tuning, Mistral fine-tuning, LLM data prep, token counter, JSONL validator, schema migrator, PII detector" />
  <meta name="author" content="convertFlow" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://convertflow.live/" />

  <!-- Open Graph -->
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="convertFlow" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="convertFlow — Free LLM Dataset Prep & RAG Chunking, In-Browser" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Convert datasets to JSONL for OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral fine-tuning. Chunk docs for RAG. 17 utilities. Free, no signup, runs in your browser." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://convertflow.live/" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://convertflow.live/og-image.png" />
  <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
  <meta property="og:image:alt" content="convertFlow — in-browser LLM dataset prep tool" />

  <!-- Twitter Card -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="convertFlow — Free LLM Dataset Prep & RAG Chunking" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Convert datasets to JSONL for fine-tuning across 14 providers. Chunk docs for RAG. 17 utilities. Free, in-browser, no signup." />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://convertflow.live/og-image.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="convertFlow — LLM dataset prep tool" />

  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="256x256" href="/favicon-256.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="512x512" href="/favicon-512.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />

  <!-- JSON-LD: WebApplication -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebApplication",
    "name": "convertFlow",
    "url": "https://convertflow.live",
    "description": "Free in-browser tool for preparing LLM fine-tuning datasets (JSONL, ChatML, Alpaca, ShareGPT, Harmony) and chunking documents for RAG. 17 utilities, multi-provider validation, no signup required.",
    "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
    "operatingSystem": "Any (Web Browser)",
    "browserRequirements": "Requires a modern browser with JavaScript enabled.",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "price": "0",
      "priceCurrency": "USD"
    },
    "featureList": [
      "JSONL fine-tuning dataset conversion",
      "Multi-provider schema validation (OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral, Llama, and 10 more)",
      "ChatML / Alpaca / ShareGPT / Harmony format migration",
      "RAG document chunking with semantic, paragraph, and fixed strategies",
      "PII detection (31 categories)",
      "Token counter and cost calculator",
      "JSONL validator and repair",
      "Dataset splitter (train/val/test)",
      "Hugging Face Hub direct push",
      "100% client-side processing"
    ],
    "creator": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "convertFlow"
    }
  })} />

  <!-- JSON-LD: FAQPage -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is convertFlow free?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. convertFlow is completely free with no signup, no account, and no usage limits. It runs entirely in your browser."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does my data leave the browser?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No. All processing happens locally in your browser. Files are never uploaded to a server. The only network calls are optional Hugging Face Hub uploads using your own access token."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which fine-tuning formats does convertFlow support?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "convertFlow supports JSONL (ChatML), Alpaca, ShareGPT, Harmony (gpt-oss), JSON, CSV, TSV, Parquet, Markdown, and plain text. It validates against schemas for 14 providers: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, Mistral, xAI, DeepSeek, Cohere, Microsoft, Alibaba, IBM, BigCode, TII, and 01.AI."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can convertFlow chunk documents for RAG?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. The Chunk tab splits documents into embedding-ready chunks using fixed-token, paragraph, or semantic strategies. It includes overlap visualization, manual boundary editing, and live embedding cost estimates across providers."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What file formats can I import?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "convertFlow accepts .txt, .md, .json, .jsonl, .csv, .tsv, .docx, .pdf, .xlsx, .png, .jpg, and other image formats (with OCR via tesseract.js). All processing is local."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How is convertFlow different from OpenPipe or Entry Point AI?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "convertFlow is 100% client-side with no signup required. Commercial platforms like OpenPipe and Entry Point AI require accounts and upload your data to their servers. convertFlow keeps everything in your browser."
        }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const t = localStorage.getItem('dataprep-theme');
      document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', t === 'light' ? 'light' : 'dark');
    })();
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="app">
    <TopBar client:load />
    <TabStrip client:load />

    <div id="panel-convert" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-convert" class="tab-panel" data-tab="convert">
      <ConvertTab client:load />
    </div>

    <div id="panel-chunk" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-chunk" class="tab-panel" data-tab="chunk" hidden>
      <ChunkTab client:load />
    </div>

    <div id="panel-editor" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-editor" class="tab-panel" data-tab="editor" hidden>
      <EditorTab client:load />
    </div>

    <div id="panel-utilities" role="tabpanel" class="tab-panel" data-tab="utilities" hidden>
      <UtilitiesTab client:load />
    </div>

    <SupportPanel client:load />
    <StatusBar client:load />
    <CommandPalette client:load />
  </div>

  <script>
    import { shellState, toggleTheme, openPalette, closePalette, setTab } from '../stores/shellState';
    import { decodeShareFragment } from '../lib/share-url';
    import { openFile } from '../stores/editorState';
    import { wireDesktopExitConfirm } from '../lib/tauri-runtime';

    // Wire Tauri-only behaviour (no-op in browser).
    wireDesktopExitConfirm();

    // Sync tab panel visibility with active tab
    shellState.subscribe((state) => {
      const panels = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.tab-panel');
      panels.forEach((panel) => {
        panel.hidden = panel.getAttribute('data-tab') !== state.activeTab;
      });
    });

    // Rehydrate theme from localStorage on mount
    const stored = localStorage.getItem('dataprep-theme');
    const theme = stored === 'light' ? 'light' : 'dark';
    document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', theme);
    shellState.update((s) => ({ ...s, theme }));

    // Restore Editor share fragment
    const payload = decodeShareFragment(location.hash);
    if (payload?.tab === 'editor') {
      openFile(payload.name, payload.content);
      setTab('editor');
    }

    // Global keyboard shortcuts (⌘ on Mac, Ctrl on Windows/Linux)
    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
      const mod = /Mac|iPhone|iPad|iPod/.test(navigator.platform || navigator.userAgent) ? e.metaKey : e.ctrlKey;
      if (mod && e.key === 't') { e.preventDefault(); toggleTheme(); }
      if (mod && e.key === 'k') { e.preventDefault(); openPalette(); }
      if (e.key === 'Escape') { closePalette(); }
    });
  </script>

  <!-- SEO content for search engines -->
  <div class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">
    <h1>convertFlow — Free Browser-Based LLM Dataset Prep Tool</h1>
    <p>convertFlow is a free, in-browser tool for preparing fine-tuning datasets and RAG document chunks for Large Language Models. No signup, no upload, no account required. Everything runs locally in your browser.</p>

    <h2>What convertFlow Does</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>JSONL fine-tuning conversion</strong> — Turn CSV, JSON, plain text, or conversation transcripts into JSONL formats accepted by OpenAI, Anthropic, Mistral, Llama, and 11 other providers.</li>
      <li><strong>Schema migration</strong> — Convert datasets between ChatML, Alpaca, ShareGPT, and Harmony (gpt-oss) formats with auto-detection and diff preview.</li>
      <li><strong>RAG document chunking</strong> — Split documents into embedding-ready chunks using fixed-token, paragraph, or semantic strategies. Includes overlap visualization and live embedding cost estimates.</li>
      <li><strong>17 bundled utilities</strong> — Token counter, cost calculator, JSON/JSONL validator, JSONL repair, dataset splitter, PII detector (31 categories), regex tester, duplicate detector, schema migrator, template expander, conversation formatter, hash generator, encoding tools, timestamp converter, and more.</li>
      <li><strong>Hugging Face Hub push</strong> — Upload datasets directly to HF from your browser using your own token. No server middleman.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Supported Fine-Tuning Formats</h2>
    <p>OpenAI ChatML, Anthropic Harmony, Alpaca instruction tuning, ShareGPT conversations, raw JSONL, JSON, CSV, TSV, Parquet, Markdown, plain text.</p>

    <h2>Supported Providers</h2>
    <p>OpenAI (GPT-4, GPT-4o, GPT-3.5), Anthropic (Claude 3.5, Claude 4), Google (Gemini), Meta (Llama 3.1, Llama 3.3), Mistral (Large 3, Mixtral), xAI (Grok), DeepSeek (V3, R1), Cohere (Command R), Microsoft (Phi-4), Alibaba (Qwen 2.5), IBM (Granite), BigCode (StarCoder), TII (Falcon), 01.AI (Yi).</p>

    <h2>Common Use Cases</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Convert OpenAI fine-tuning JSONL to Anthropic Harmony format</li>
      <li>Migrate Alpaca instruction datasets to ShareGPT format</li>
      <li>Split documents into RAG chunks before vector embedding</li>
      <li>Validate JSONL files against OpenAI, Anthropic, or Mistral schemas</li>
      <li>Detect and redact PII before training</li>
      <li>Count tokens across multiple model tokenizers</li>
      <li>Estimate embedding costs before running on large datasets</li>
      <li>Repair malformed JSONL files (trailing commas, single quotes, truncated lines)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why convertFlow</h2>
    <p>Most fine-tuning data prep tools require signup, upload your data to their servers, or only support OpenAI. convertFlow is the only tool that bundles JSONL conversion, RAG chunking, multi-provider validation, schema migration, and 17 utilities — all running 100% in your browser with zero data ever leaving your machine.</p>

    <h2>Open the Tool</h2>
    <p>Use the four tabs above: Convert for fine-tuning data, Chunk for RAG documents, Editor for hand-editing JSONL, Utilities for token counting, validation, and other tools. Press ⌘K / Ctrl+K to open the command palette. <a href="/help">Read the full guide</a> or <a href="/about">learn more</a>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0,0,0,0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  #app {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100dvh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .tab-panel {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 0;
  }
  .tab-panel[hidden] { display: none; }
</style>
